  "name": "ACL Config Generator",
  "description": "Generates Cisco ACL configurations from DNS/DHCP server IP lists. Supports both web form input (paste IPs) and webhook API (JSON). Output includes DNS, DHCP, SSH, HTTPS, ICMP rules with explicit deny.",
