  "diagram_notes": [
    {
      "content": "--- Generated ACL ---\n\nip access-list extended FILTER-IN\n\n  remark Allow DNS (UDP/TCP 53) to DNS/DHCP servers\n  permit udp any host 1.1.1.1 eq domain\n  permit tcp any host 1.1.1.1 eq domain\n  permit udp any host 2.2.2.2 eq domain\n  permit tcp any host 2.2.2.2 eq domain\n  permit udp any host 3.3.3.3 eq domain\n  permit tcp any host 3.3.3.3 eq domain\n\n  remark Allow DHCP (client <-> server)\n  permit udp any eq bootpc host 1.1.1.1 eq bootps\n  permit udp host 1.1.1.1 eq bootps any eq bootpc\n  permit udp any eq bootpc host 2.2.2.2 eq bootps\n  permit udp host 2.2.2.2 eq bootps any eq bootpc\n  permit udp any eq bootpc host 3.3.3.3 eq bootps\n  permit udp host 3.3.3.3 eq bootps any eq bootpc\n\n  remark Allow SSH and HTTPS to the servers\n  permit tcp any host 1.1.1.1 eq 22\n  permit tcp any host 1.1.1.1 eq 443\n  permit tcp any host 2.2.2.2 eq 22\n  permit tcp any host 2.2.2.2 eq 443\n  permit tcp any host 3.3.3.3 eq 22\n  permit tcp any host 3.3.3.3 eq 443\n\n  remark Allow ICMP to the servers\n  permit icmp any host 1.1.1.1\n  permit icmp any host 2.2.2.2\n  permit icmp any host 3.3.3.3\n\n  remark Explicit deny everything else\n  deny ip any any log",
      "position": [
        690,
        240
      ],
      "guid": "8fec4c45c2adc0463cbb81d9e0a96a4b",
      "width": 290
    },
    {
      "content": "# ACL Config Generator\n\nThis story generates Cisco ACL configurations from a list of DNS/DHCP server IPs.\n\n## Two Input Methods:\n\n### 1. Web Form (Page Action)\n- Visit the page URL\n- Paste IPs in the text field (one per line)\n- Click Submit\n\n### 2. Webhook API\n- POST to the webhook URL\n- Send JSON: `{\"dns_ips\": [\"ip1\", \"ip2\", ...]}`\n- Requires ACL_WEBHOOK_SECRET credential\n\n## Output\nThe generated ACL config includes:\n- DNS (UDP/TCP port 53)\n- DHCP (client ↔ server)\n- SSH (port 22) and HTTPS (port 443)\n- ICMP\n- Explicit deny all",
      "position": [
        -510,
        -120
      ],
      "guid": "1657f8e1f10a03ff8c7fc5561ca449eb",
      "width": 280
    },
    {
      "content": "## Web Form Input\n\n**Page URL:** Click the page action to get the URL\n\n**Format:** One IP address per line\n\nExample:\n```\n192.168.10.10\n192.168.10.11\n192.168.10.12\n```",
      "position": [
        -210,
        -90
      ],
      "guid": "c5a775feac8db54a4866224389507f9a",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "content": "## Webhook Input\n\n**Webhook URL:** Click the webhook action to get the URL\n\n**Method:** POST\n\n**Headers:**\n- `Content-Type: application/json`\n\n**Body:**\n```json\n{\n  \"dns_ips\": [\n    \"192.168.10.10\",\n    \"192.168.10.11\",\n    \"192.168.10.12\"\n  ]\n}\n```",
      "position": [
        705,
        -210
      ],
      "guid": "5966c17486a1e5f86b0b352a8a1ba094",
      "width": 250
    }
  ],
